<p>In below code, abc-1.1.2.jar file present under the  <code>${webapps.dir}/App.ear/App.war/WEB-INF/lib/</code> folder.</p>  <pre><code>&lt;foreach target="updateApp" param="detectedApp"&gt;     &lt;path&gt;         &lt;dirset dir="${webapps.dir}"&gt;             &lt;present targetdir="${webapps.dir}"&gt;                 &lt;!-- All Web apps should have this folder containing abcd-*.jar --&gt;                 &lt;mapper type="regexp"                     from="^(.*)/abcd([0-9.-]*)\.jar$$"                     to="\1/abcd\2.jar"/&gt;             &lt;/present&gt;         &lt;/dirset&gt;     &lt;/path&gt; &lt;/foreach&gt; </code></pre>